      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm looking at some audit numbers from the rotterdam warehouse and something is off. we've got a recurring mismatch between our ERP records and the physical count for certain electronic components. can you help me figure out what might be causing these small discrepancies?\n\nhere is the data from the last three counts:\n\nPart ID | ERP Count | Physical Count | Variance\nSKU-9928 | 1,402 | 1,398 | -4\nSKU-4410 | 850 | 847 | -3\nSKU-1105 | 2,115 | 2,111 | -4\nSKU-7732 | 540 | 538 | -2",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
